                                <strong>Small Group Sizes</strong> - Personalized attention
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="icon fa fa-check"></span>
                                <strong>Safe Environment</strong> - Fully supervised activities
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="icon fa fa-check"></span>
                                <strong>Flexible Scheduling</strong> - Options to fit your needs
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>

                    <div class="contact-info mt-5">
                        <h4>Questions? Contact Us:</h4>
                        <ul class="registration-contact-list">
                            <li>
                                <i class="icon flaticon-call"></i>
